msgstr "The optimal distance is 15 meters. The maximum communication distance between a base station and a tag can reach 60 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:432 e9d78997b29e46f19e36454a35566cdc
msgid "UWB模组除了定位功能之外，支持数据传输吗？"
msgstr "Besides positioning, does the UWB module support data transmission?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:433 bde11291547a445ca13ec2db6c7cf133
msgid "UWB模组支持数据传输"
msgstr "The UWB module supports data transmission."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:436 7cede7264fc64b65961c23e66fbea208
msgid "UWB模块如果需要做问的精确的定位，一般间隔多少米布置一个基站"
msgstr "If the UWB module needs to perform relatively accurate positioning, what is the typical spacing for deploying base stations?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:437 ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:496 721ba0f3c054493a8aea08530661af82 eeada9fe187a4471a9a9dedec1ca3099
msgid "15米"
msgstr "15 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:440 b75ccd634f124afa94ed4dac28abbb04
