msgstr "Can the UWB module be driven by a coin cell battery?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:441 19697a56e3d44365a43a4312bfe5d8c4
msgid "不可以，驱动电流不足；建议使用3.3V稳定的供电电源"
msgstr "No. The drive current is insufficient; it is recommended to use a stable 3.3 V power supply."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:444 22e1fa413d8b47a2b66741fbed9fa433
msgid "BU01开发板支持哪些烧写方式"
msgstr "What flashing methods does the BU01 development board support?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:445 902b010671f4460a9d4f16332223aee5
msgid "jink、stlink等支持SWD的烧写方式"
msgstr "J-Link, ST-Link, and other flashing methods that support SWD."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:448 3d9d3eff3dd8442e9a326e41a0006d37
msgid "BU-01模组可以指定主从模式吗？"
