#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:449 88d2e8047ac14ef2993f95b064f08ffb
msgid "BU-01为纯射频模块，不带MCU，我们BU-01开发板的固件就有做主从机的功能。详情查看我们官网的文档。"
msgstr "BU-01 is a pure RF module without an MCU. The firmware of our BU-01 development board implements master/slave functionality. For details, please refer to our official documentation."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:454 0ceb6104e3f44575bd2efde008f98d75
msgid "UWB通讯最远多远？"
msgstr "What is the farthest UWB communication distance?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:455 c6f9deb6dea54f35a07e1ba047c95629
msgid "60米"
msgstr "60 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:458 65aa5785310043c3b0e4e14c8dd49c60
msgid "请问BU-01有TDOA定位算法的demo么？"
msgstr "Does BU-01 have a demo for the TDOA positioning algorithm?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:459 90f80385e4664e8fba40e2fdbd712878
msgid "没有，只要TWR定位算法。"
msgstr "No. It only has the TWR positioning algorithm."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:462 f89e7e2ccbf545deb9ac4dca81e3697c
