msgstr "One is set as a base station, and the other is set as a tag."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:470 b52732f6a8fc4aa8a1c49402ace89ae8
msgid "BU01开发板一个能用吗"
msgstr "Can one BU01 development board be used alone?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:471 ca5aee034e5a47cda98785058ed1f7c5
msgid "不可以，测距至少需要2个才能正常测试"
msgstr "No. At least 2 boards are required for normal ranging tests."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:474 c3f59612a385417eba6157ed2069fe5b
msgid "请问一下，为什么我用C8T6单片机烧录定位程序驱动BU-01模组，但是程序启动不起来？"
msgstr "Why does the program fail to start when I use a C8T6 MCU to flash the positioning program and drive the BU-01 module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:475 01d967e482434964a39b5cc5c9e73609
msgid "该程序适配的是我们BU-01开发板，开发板晶振用的是16M的，因此要用16M晶振的开发板驱动即可；"
msgstr "This program is adapted for our BU-01 development board. The development board uses a 16 MHz crystal, so it can be driven by a development board with a 16 MHz crystal."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:478 c29cc220279647a5b824de31f06a3026
msgid "你好，请问一下，BU-01模组的驱动库是否可移植？"
msgstr "Hello, is the driver library of the BU-01 module portable?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:479 0e34d8ba16da4e98b033ab3c7543d50a
msgid "用STM32驱动的源码是开放的，可以直接移植其中驱动BU-01的库； `源码获取链接  <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/uwb>`__"
msgstr "The STM32 driver source code is open, and the library for driving BU-01 can be directly ported. `Source code link  <https://docs.ai-thinker.com/uwb>`__"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:483 573530831f52446e94d5a179714a50b8
msgid "请问我用单片机驱动BU-01模组写进去数据之后等待发送完成却迟迟不成功是什么原因呢？"
msgstr "Why does sending data fail to complete when I use an MCU to drive the BU-01 module and wait for transmission completion?"

