msgstr "It is suspected that there is an issue with the SPI bus driver. Please check whether the driver is normal. (SPI write code)"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:487 7773e4ced39240e0b99cac0524d4beea
msgid "UWB开发板能同时采集加速度和UWB数据吗"
msgstr "Can the UWB development board collect acceleration and UWB data at the same time?"

