msgid "可以同时采集"
msgstr "Yes, it can collect both at the same time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:491 ddd9f4f198c04de481ccd7bc73975615
msgid "UWB模块如何实现睡眠模式下功耗小于1mA"
msgstr "How can the UWB module achieve power consumption below 1 mA in sleep mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:492 73b67e7114d04d58bf0537102e61ffc0
msgid "模块可以使用MCU进行SPI读写相关寄存器来实现"
msgstr "The module can use the MCU to read and write relevant registers via SPI to achieve this."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:495 87ca4d9d67d047ce9617dc3e7e439133
msgid "UWB模块如果需要定位准确，建议多少米部署一个基站"
msgstr "For accurate positioning with the UWB module, what spacing is recommended for deploying base stations?"

