msgid "UWB开发板在移动后会有一个大约5秒的延迟，该如何优化"
msgstr "There is about a 5-second delay after the UWB development board moves. How can this be optimized?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:500 3cd2208682fa4fba8f30958a6eb5dd2b
msgid "可以通过修改内部的程序进行实现，因为开发板在移动后会重新计算定位的坐标参数值。"
msgstr "It can be implemented by modifying the internal program, because after the development board moves, it recalculates the positioning coordinate parameters."

