msgid "UWB开发板上设置测距间隔5-20是什么单位"
msgstr "What is the unit of the ranging interval setting 5-20 on the UWB development board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:504 2f77e8243b9f45a3bebe3091379bf5c2
msgid "采集次数，值越大刷新速度越慢"
msgstr "Number of acquisition times. The larger the value, the slower the refresh rate."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:507 acf41cadc0c746caaa6a0d4046cb3b00
msgid "UWB是室内室外都可以用吗"
msgstr "Can UWB be used both indoors and outdoors?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:508 c6c6eea7b4324b2d95eb8adb8629cd59
msgid "是的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:511 e012ece4411540e880d430457db34f03
msgid "使用BU-01开发板做定位的话，需要买几个？"
msgstr "How many BU-01 development boards should I buy for positioning?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:512 03ed4a222ac74e519054f728f2d7a5a9
msgid "一个标签，加3个基站，共4个；"
msgstr "One tag plus three base stations, four in total."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:515 f19387376a34497eaa796529345df35a
msgid "BU01模块可以和其他不同牌子的UWB模块通信吗"
msgstr "Can the BU01 module communicate with UWB modules of other brands?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:519 fddd12db39f64d10abc8cb855c57460c
msgid "BU01开发板可以引导小车吗"
msgstr "Can the BU01 development board guide a cart?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:520 2e5b7338825a40039f375c03bd8e6c18
msgid "可以，通过二次开发的方式进行实现"
msgstr "Yes. It can be implemented through secondary development."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:523 d0c00ad9e1684c97a039584b92ab2559
msgid "请问UWB基站应用部署一般需要几个呢？"
msgstr "How many base stations are generally needed for UWB base station deployment?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:524 43799a56678c4f9982a9417ed1ae4df2
msgid "至少需要3个以上基站。"
msgstr "At least 3 base stations are required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:527 52a57f97d3084efca5ff9b84f19f86f3
msgid "UWB开发板在在一标签三基站的情况下，为什么只有标签端串口有返回值"
msgstr "In a one-tag-three-base-station setup with the UWB development board, why does only the tag-side serial port return values?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:528 1844a52724bd4980a78c5f574dd736c1
msgid "因为只有0号基站才会输出距离信息，其他ID号的基站不会输出"
msgstr "Because only base station No. 0 outputs distance information. Base stations with other IDs do not output it."

