msgid "目前代码处理已经是最快的频率，输出频率可以通过AT+interval指令将数值设置到5进行测试  5已经是上限值了  这个值是获取测距数据次数   范围为5-50次  值越大刷新速度越慢"
msgstr "The current code processing is already at the fastest frequency. The output frequency can be tested by setting the value to 5 through the AT+interval command. 5 is already the upper limit. This value is the number of times ranging data is obtained. The range is 5-50 times; the larger the value, the slower the refresh rate."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:543 8a003e978c274259b1b5377892e71af5
msgid "UWB开发板上的加速度传感器还需要额外接入吗"
msgstr "Does the accelerometer on the UWB development board need to be connected separately?"

