msgid "不需要，我们出厂的板子已经焊接好温湿度和加速度传感器"
msgstr "No. Our factory board already has the temperature/humidity sensor and accelerometer soldered."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:547 53529bf6916547cf9670985c7ffb2665
msgid "请问BU-01模组的三个VCC是否一样的，能否连接在一起？"
msgstr "Are the three VCC pins of the BU-01 module the same? Can they be connected together?"

