msgid "请问BU-01能否做到两个设备实现定位功能？"
msgstr "Can BU-01 achieve positioning with two devices?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/UWB/index.rst:552 7fb9c70ce27c4d10acfa0ef3ef7f55fc
msgid "两个设备做不到，至少需要三个基站给标签做定位功能。"
msgstr "No. Two devices cannot do positioning. At least three base stations are required to position a tag."
